  "title": "📦LONG TERM WAREHOUSE ASSISTANTS NEEDED📦 (ADT)",
  "description": "<p>📦LONG TERM WAREHOUSE ASSISTANTS NEEDED📦</p><p></p><p>🚉 Location: Changi South (Near Expo MRT)</p><p>⏰ Hours: 5.5 Days, Mon to Fri 8am to 5pm & Sat, 9am to 1pm or 11am to 3pm</p><p>💰Salary: $1800 to $2300/month</p><p></p><p>📝Job Scope</p><p>📦 Picking, packing & sorting of items</p><p>📦 Sort and pick missing items</p><p>📦 Assist in daily shipping and receiving operations</p><p>📦 Support inventory tracking and stock management</p><p>📦 Prepare and maintain logistics documents (e.g., delivery orders, invoices)</p><p>📦 Update and manage data in inventory</p><p>📦 Other general warehouse duties</p><p></p><p>Applicants who are interested, pls email to recruit@onehirestaffing.com or call 6031 4933</p><p>1. Full Name</p><p>2. Residential Location</p><p>3. Start/End Date</p><p></p><p>R1104563 (Tan Si Ni Shirley Gwen)</p><p>EA License: 25C3058 (One Hire Staffing Pte Ltd)</p>",
